				<p>We'll set up one for working from home and one to ring your cell phone when you're out of the office. So, the first thing we're going to do is set up two <a href="https://www.fastmetrics.com/support/cloud-phone-service-time-frames/" title="time frames" class="orange_link" target="_blank">time frames</a>. So, just click on time frames. Click add time frame.</p>
				<p>We want these rules to apply all the time, so we can toggle them from our default rule, which will probably ring our desk phone to our cell phone or, our home rule.</p>
